CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 20, 1962, pg. 1 reads:"President Kennedy Stumps Area For Democrats - At Greater Pittsburgh Airport the President is shown being greeted by the many police officers who guarded him."
TitMainTitle: Police officers greeting John F. Kennedy at airport with Air Force One in background
